  m_text: 'Dear Dylon Smith,


    Congratulations! We are excited to formally offer
    you the position of Interstellar Space Flight Pilot at Unified Transplanetary
    Corporation. Your passion, skills, and experience align perfectly with our vision
    for pushing the boundaries of space exploration.


    Your selection reflects
    our confidence in your ability to contribute significantly to our pioneering
    efforts. As an Interstellar Space Flight Pilot, you''ll be a vital part of our
    mission to revolutionize interstellar space travel.


    We are eager to have
    you on board and look forward to embarking on this journey together. Please electronically
    sign on the field below. Our HR team will assist you through the onboarding process,
    ensuring a smooth transition into our team of dedicated professionals.



'
